                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <desc type="PurchaseNote"/>
                           <locus target="#152r"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">
                              ዝመጽሐፍ። ዘአጥረዮ፡ ሐብተ፡ 
                                 <sic>ማረያም፡</sic>
                               በእንተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ 
                                 <sic>በነዋዩ።</sic>
                              
                           </q>
                           <note>
                              The note states that the book was purchased by <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11516HabtaMa">Habta Māryām</persName>.
                           </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <desc type="MagicText">Magic formula to protect the labour</desc>
                           <locus target="#152v"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">ዝክዝ፡ ኪድሮስ። ኪርሀም። በዝንቱ፡ አስማቲከ፡ ዘያርሕዎ፡ 
                                 <sic>
                                    <supplied reason="omitted">ለ</supplied>ማሐጸን፡</sic>
                               
                              አርሕዎ፡ <supplied reason="omitted">ለ</supplied>ማሕጸና፡ ለአመትከ፡</q>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <desc type="ProtectivePrayer"/>
                           <locus target="#152v"/>
                           <note>The prayer begins as follows: 
                              <q xml:lang="gez">ወበስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩፡ 
                                    <sic>አምለከ፡</sic>
                                  ኣደናኤል፡ አደርዊ፡ አደታዊ።</q>, 
                              and terminates as follows: <q xml:lang="gez">በከመ፡ 
                                    <sic>እይቅርብው፡</sic>
                                  ለገብርከ፡ ሐብተ፡ ማርያም።</q>. 
                              It is meant to protect <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11516HabtaMa">Habta Māryām</persName>.
                           </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <desc type="OwnershipNote"/>
                           <locus target="#153v"/>
                           <q xml:lang="ar">
                              الحمد لله رب العالم صك بهده الم...  طالع بهذه الكتاب المقدس العبد الفقير الى الله تعالى كاتب هذه الاحرط ... معحب داوود بن اندراوس المنبيدي فسبح لله تعالي في روءوس ... امين 
                           </q>
                           <note>
                              The note is written in Arabic.
                           </note>
                        </item>
                        
                        <item xml:id="e1">
                           <desc>The previous shelfmark <q xml:lang="la">Assem<supplied reason="explanation">anianus n° 91. inter arabicos</supplied>
                              </q> is 
                              written on the inner side of the front board, together with the current shelfmarks <q>69</q> (erased) and <q>70</q>.</desc>
                        </item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
